JSON-RPC2-AnyEvent-Client version 0.1.0

This module implement JSON RPC2 nonblocking client based on
AnyEvent tcp transport implementation.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

 JSON::XS
 JSON::RPC2::Client
 AnyEvent::Handle


